{
  "message": "test(raptorq): exercise F6 wavefront invariants with missing symbols\n\nChange three F6 tests (f6_first_decode_is_stable_with_zero_deltas,\nf6_window_bounded_across_decodes, f6_retuning_deltas_always_bounded)\nfrom k=8 with all symbols present to k=16 with symbol drops\n([0, 3, 7] + 4 extra repair symbols).\n\nThe previous trivial all-present configuration did not exercise the\ndecoder's wavefront pipeline under realistic conditions where source\nsymbols are lost and must be recovered from repair symbols. The new\nparameters validate the invariants with actual erasure recovery.\n\nUpdate wavefront pipeline JSON artifact with new measurement values\nfrom the re-run.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
